headline: NetApp Hosts First Quarter of Fiscal Year 2026 Financial Results Webcast
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., July 31, 2025--After market close on August 27, 2025, NetApp (NASDAQ: NTAP) will announce financial results for the first quarter of fiscal year 2026, which ended July 25, 2025.
